;s school supplies, household essentials for their family or just something they&#39;ve had on their wish list for themselves, most teachers will find a way to spend a few extra dollars at Amazon (or <a data-i13n="cpos:39;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Walmart;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=3719d8d4-5edd-4817-998a-91f3229e7323&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Walmart&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASKZeBuhjSh07MprzcvpUGK2BxBoKVQIr8twvBA3r4rq&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FBasic-Blue-Yellow-Spark-Walmart-Gift-Card%2F654950389%3Fathbdg%3DL1600">Walmart</a> , <a data-i13n="cpos:40;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Target;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=827d7835-78d6-4491-ae04-c042cab1d6e7&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Target&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI4MjdkNzgzNS03OGQ2LTQ0OTEtYWUwNC1jMDQyY2FiMWQ2ZTciLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGFyZ2V0LmNvbS9jL3RhcmdldC1naWZ0Y2FyZHMtZ2lmdC1jYXJkcy8tL04tNXhzeHQiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjY0NzljZjc3LWExZTYtNDdjMi05NzU4LWJmNWRjZTAxZmZiMyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAARsmNzljmGD9iZ4Nq37slJ9G6PiFuSzPqukmHh0pJ9ds&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fc%2Ftarget-giftcards-gift-cards%2F-%2FN-5xsxt">Target</a> or another retailer they prefer). <em>— 副总裁</em></p><h2>A relaxing video game or two </h2><p><core-commerce id="9b7d37d01ccb4e55a38f8e2a751f37a2" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> If your kid&#39;s teacher likes to wind down with a video game after an aggravating day of work, a recommendation from our list of <a data-i13n="cpos:41;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-relaxing-video-games-140048572.html">good relaxing games</a> could make for a gift that&#39;s both thoughtful and fun. A couple of standouts: <a data-i13n="cpos:42;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shoppi